#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktuberling; offers a gentle and rewarding introduction to &kde; "
"customization and programming. The application can be extended. For example, "
"without any coding, new playgrounds can be added by changing the graphics "
"files. By adding appropriate sound files, translators can change the sounds "
"to their native tongue!"
msgstr ""
"&ktuberling; &kde; अनुकूलनं प्रोग्रामिंग् च। अनुप्रयोगस्य विस्तारः कर्तुं शक्यते। यथा, किमपि "
"कोडिंग् विना, ग्राफिक्स् सञ्चिकाः परिवर्त्य नूतनानि क्रीडाङ्गणानि योजयितुं शक्यन्ते । "
"समुचितध्वनिसञ्चिकाः योजयित्वा अनुवादकाः ध्वनयः स्वदेशीयभाषायां परिवर्तयितुं शक्नुवन्ति!"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you extend or add to the game please consider sending your additions to "
"the maintainer <ulink url=\"mailto:alex@eyeos.org\">Alex Fiestas</ulink> for "
"inclusion in future releases."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् क्रीडायां विस्तारं करोति वा योजयति वा तर्हि कृपया भविष्ये विमोचनेषु समावेशार्थं "
"भवतः परिवर्तनं परिपालकं <ulink url=\"mailto:alex@eyeos.org\">Alex Fiestas</"
"ulink> प्रेषयितुं विचारयतु"

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Artists"
msgstr "कलाकारानां कृते"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new &ktuberling; playground you have to:"
msgstr "नूतनं &ktuberling; क्रीडाङ्गणं भवद्भिः कर्तव्यम् अस्ति :"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw the playground in a &SVG; file, there you have to:"
msgstr "क्रीडाङ्गणं &SVG; file, तत्र भवता कर्तव्यं:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name the place where items can dragged <quote>background</quote>."
msgstr "यत्र वस्तूनि <quote>पृष्ठभूमि</quote> कर्षितुं शक्यन्ते तस्य स्थानस्य नामकरणं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name each of the draggable items with an unique name."
msgstr "कर्षणीयवस्तूनाम् प्रत्येकं अद्वितीयनाम्ना नामकरणं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal> file, it has to follow "
"this schema:"
msgstr ""
"<literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal> सञ्चिकां रचयन्तु, एतस्याः योजनायाः "
"अनुसरणं कर्तव्यम् अस्ति:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;playground gameboard=\"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable>\" name="
"\"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;object name=\"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable>\" sound="
"\"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>\" scale=\"<replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/playground&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;playground gameboard=\"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable>\" name="
"\"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>डेस्कटॉपसञ्चिका</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;object name=\"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>वस्तूनाम्</replaceable>\" sound="
"\"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>ध्वनिनाम</replaceable>\" scale=\"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>किञ्चित्मूल्यं</"
"replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/क्रीडाङ्गण&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable> is the name of the &SVG; file that "
"has the drawing."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable> इति &SVG; सञ्चिका यस्याः रेखाचित्रम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable> is the name of the desktop file "
"that has the name of the theme."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable> इति विषयस्य नाम यस्य डेस्कटॉप् "
"सञ्चिकायाः नाम अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each object you need a <literal>&lt;object&gt;</literal> entry. "
"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable> is the unique name you used on the &SVG; "
"file, <replaceable>soundName</replaceable> is the sound name that will be "
"played when dragging it, see the <filename>sounds/soundthemes.HOWTO</"
"filename> file from source code for more information."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं वस्तुनः कृते भवतः <literal>&lt;object&gt;</literal> प्रविष्टिः आवश्यकी भवति । "
"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable> इति अद्वितीयं नाम भवता &SVG; file, "
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable> इति ध्वनिनाम यत् तत् कर्षति समये वाद्यते, "
"अधिकसूचनार्थं स्रोतसङ्केतः <filename>sounds/soundthemes.HOWTO</filename> सञ्चिकां "
"पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>scale</literal> is optional and <replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable> is the scale factor that will be used when drawing this object "
"outside the warehouse, if not specified is 1."
msgstr ""
"<literal>scale</literal> वैकल्पिकं भवति तथा च <replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable> इति स्केलकारकं यत् गोदामात् बहिः एतत् वस्तु आकर्षयन्ते सति उपयुज्यते, यदि "
"निर्दिष्टं न भवति तर्हि 1 अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> file, it has to "
"follow this schema:"
msgstr ""
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> सञ्चिकां रचयन्तु, एतस्याः योजनायाः "
"अनुसरणं कर्तव्यम् अस्ति:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[KTuberlingTheme]\n"
"Name=<replaceable>themeName</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"[KTuberlingTheme] ९.\n"
"Name=<replaceable>themeName</replaceable> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>themeName</replaceable> is the name that identifies the theme, "
"will be shown in the Playground menu."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>themeName</replaceable> इति नाम यत् विषयस्य परिचयं करोति, "
"Playground मेन्यू मध्ये दर्शितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adding the theme to &ktuberling; repository, add <literal role="
"\"extension\">.svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, "
"and <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files to <literal>FILES</"
"literal> section of the <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> into the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">pics/</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &ktuberling; भण्डारं, <literal role=\"extension\">.svg</literal>, "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, तथा <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.desktop</literal> सञ्चिकाः योजयन्तु <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> "
"इत्यस्य <literal>FILES</literal> विभागस्य <filename class=\"directory\">pics/</"
"filename> इत्यत्र पुटम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to install it for yourself, place <literal role=\"extension\">."
"svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, and <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files into the <filename class="
"\"directory\">ktuberling/pics</filename> folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् स्वयमेव संस्थापयितुम् इच्छति तर्हि स्थापयतु<literal role=\"extension\"> .स्वग्</"
"literal> , ९.<literal role=\"extension\"> ।विषयवस्तु</literal> , तथा<literal "
"role=\"extension\"> .डेस्कटॉप्</literal> सञ्चिकाः मध्ये<filename class=\"directory"
"\"> ktuberling/pics</filename> folder in<userinput><command> qtpaths इति</"
"command><option value=\"--paths GenericDataLocation\"> --paths "
"सामान्यदत्तांशस्थान</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Translators"
msgstr "अनुवादकानां कृते"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the usual <literal role=\"extension\">.po</literal> files mechanism "
"for translating program labels and prompts, the sounds can be localized too."
msgstr ""
"प्रोग्राम् लेबल् तथा प्रॉम्प्ट् इत्येतयोः अनुवादार्थं सामान्यस्य <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.po</literal> सञ्चिकातन्त्रस्य अतिरिक्तं ध्वनयः अपि स्थानीयकरणं कर्तुं शक्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new &ktuberling; sound theme you have to:"
msgstr "नूतनं &ktuberling; ध्वनि विषयः भवद्भिः :"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record the sounds in OGG Vorbis rc3 file format."
msgstr "ध्वनयः OGG Vorbis rc3 सञ्चिकास्वरूपेण रिकार्ड् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> file, it has to follow this schema:"
msgstr ""
"<filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>.soundtheme</"
"filename> सञ्चिकां रचयन्तु, एतस्याः योजनायाः अनुसरणं कर्तव्यम् अस्ति:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;language code=\"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>"
"\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;sound name=\"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>\" file="
"\"<replaceable>relativePath</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/language&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;language code=\"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>"
"\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;sound name=\"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>ध्वनिनाम</replaceable>\" file="
"\"<प्रतिस्थापनीय>सापेक्षमार्ग</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/भाषा&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> is your language two "
"letter code, for example gl for Galician."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> भवतः भाषायाः "
"द्विवर्णसङ्केतः अस्ति, उदाहरणार्थं गैलिशियन् कृते gl ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each sound a <literal>&lt;sound&gt;</literal> entry. "
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable> should match with the soundName "
"specified in the playground theme (see the <filename>pics/themes.HOWTO</"
"filename> from source code). <replaceable>relativePath</replaceable> should "
"be the relative path you are going to install the file with this sound to, "
"typically it will be <filename><replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>.<replaceable>format</replaceable></"
"filename> (<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable> can be your language "
"two letter code for example)."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं शब्दस्य कृते <literal>&lt;sound&gt;</literal> प्रविष्टिः । "
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable> इत्यनेन क्रीडाङ्गणविषये निर्दिष्टेन soundName "
"इत्यनेन सह मेलनं कर्तव्यम् (स्रोतसङ्केतः <filename>pics/themes.HOWTO</filename> पश्यन्तु) "
"। <replaceable>relativePath</replaceable> सः सापेक्षमार्गः भवितुम् अर्हति यस्मिन् "
"भवन्तः एतत् ध्वनियुक्तं सञ्चिकां संस्थापयितुं गच्छन्ति, सामान्यतया एतत् "
"<filename><replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable>/<replaceable>soundName</"
"replaceable> भविष्यति <replaceable>format</replaceable></filename> "
"(<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable> भवतः भाषा द्वौ अक्षरौ भवितुम् अर्हति "
"कोड् उदाहरणार्थम्)।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adding the sound theme to &ktuberling; in your language folder:"
msgstr "यदि भवान् &ktuberling; भवतः भाषापुटे :"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the sound files and the <literal role=\"extension\">.soundtheme</"
"literal> files into the <filename class=\"directory\">data/kdegames/"
"ktuberling</filename> folder of your language translations."
msgstr ""
"ध्वनिसञ्चिकाः <literal role=\"extension\">.soundtheme</literal> सञ्चिकाः च "
"स्वभाषाअनुवादानाम् <filename class=\"directory\">data/kdegames/ktuberling</"
"filename> पुटे योजयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On that very same dir you need a <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> file "
"describing how to install the files, typically it will be."
msgstr ""
"तस्मिन् एव dir मध्ये भवद्भ्यः <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> सञ्चिका आवश्यकी यत् "
"सञ्चिकाः कथं संस्थापनीयाः इति वर्णयति, सामान्यतया एतत् भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"FILE( GLOB oggfiles *.ogg )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES ${oggfiles} DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES <replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/sounds/ )"
msgstr ""
"FILE( GLOB oggfiles *.ogg ) 1.1.\n"
"INSTALL( FILES ${oggfiles} DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/"
"ध्वनयः/<प्रतिस्थापनीय>भवतःभाषाद्विअक्षरकोड</replaceable> )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES <replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>.ध्वनिविषय "
"DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/ध्वनयः/ )"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to install it for yourself:"
msgstr "यदि भवान् स्वयमेव संस्थापयितुम् इच्छति तर्हि :"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place <filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> file into the <filename class=\"directory\">ktuberling/"
"sounds</filename> folder in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--"
"paths GenericDataLocation</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"स्थानम्‌<filename><replaceable> yourLanguageTwoLetterCode इति</replaceable> ."
"ध्वनिविषयः</filename> file into the<filename class=\"directory\"> ktuberling/"
"ध्वनयः</filename> folder in<userinput><command> qtpaths इति</command><option "
"value=\"--paths GenericDataLocation\"> --paths सामान्यदत्तांशस्थान</option></"
"userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place your sound files into the <filename class=\"directory\">ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable></filename> folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"मध्ये स्वस्य ध्वनिसञ्चिकाः स्थापयन्तु<filename class=\"directory\"> ktuberling/ध्वनयः/ "
"२.<replaceable> someUniquePath इति</replaceable></filename> folder "
"in<userinput><command> qtpaths इति</command><option value=\"--paths "
"GenericDataLocation\"> --paths सामान्यदत्तांशस्थान</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information on how to work with the translation mechanisms in &kde; is "
"available in <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/docs/translation-howto/index."
"html\">The &kde; Translation HOWTO</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"अनुवादतन्त्रैः सह कथं कार्यं कर्तव्यमिति सूचना &kde; <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/"
"docs/translation-howto/index.html\">इत्यत्र उपलभ्यते &kde; अनुवादः HOWTO</ulink> "
"इति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Programmers"
msgstr "प्रोग्रामरस्य कृते"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ktuberling; isn't really difficult to extend for programmers."
msgstr "&ktuberling; प्रोग्रामर-कृते विस्तारयितुं वस्तुतः कठिनं न भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "C++ classes"
msgstr "C++ वर्गाः"

#. Tag: classname
#: technical-reference.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "TopLevel"
msgstr "TopLevel"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:172
